f(x)=||xa+c||_2=\sqrt{\sum_i (xa_i+c_i)^2}\geq 0
g(x)=f^2(x)
 \frac{d}{dx}g(x)=0\Rightarrow \sum_i2(xa_i+c_i)a_i=0, 
 \sum_i(xa_i^2+a_ic_i)=x\sum a^2_i+\sum a_ic_i=0, 
 x=-\frac{\sum a_ic_i}{\sum a^2_i}=-\frac{a\cdot c}{||a||_2^2}. 
{\bf a}\neq 0
